These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-1::.
2 different pets are kept: mouse, hamster
1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
2. the owner of the hamster is not to the right of the owner of the hamster##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2  |
| Pet   | hamster | mouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-2::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, cooking
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is not to the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Hobby   | cooking | filmmaking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-3::.
City: boston, colone
1. the person traveling to boston is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to colone##5
2. the person traveling to colone is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
3. the person traveling to boston is not to the right of the person traveling to boston##8

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |
| City   | boston | colone |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-4::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, montecristo
1. the alhambra-smoker is not to the right of the alhambra-smoker##8
2. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |
| Cigar   | alhambra | montecristo |

 #################################

 
